expected_tape = ['1', '2', '3', '4', '4', '3', '2', '1']
tape = TapeCallbackFunction()
p = Pipeline([Identity(), TransformCallbackStep(tape.callback, ['1']),
    TransformCallbackStep(tape.callback, ['2']), TransformCallbackStep(tape
    .callback, ['3']), TransformCallbackStep(tape.callback, ['4']), Identity()]
    )
p, _ = p.fit_transform(np.ones((1, 1)))
print('[mutating]')
p = p.mutate(new_method='inverse_transform', method_to_assign_to='transform')
p.transform(np.ones((1, 1)))
assert expected_tape == tape.get_name_tape()
